The GLO provides the public a means to perform searches for land patents by name.  In addition, the GLO is a preservation process for the aging land documents.  The GLO provides a web-based access for query, image viewing and e-commerce of the Federal Land Records</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>{"federal land records"</dcat:keyword>
